description: EndpointResource: Table containing metadata about Ericsson RAN network resources; dateTime: Timestamp of record; Area_Name: Name of the RAN area; CellId: Unique identifier for the cell site; Id2: Duplicate of CellId; Id3: seemingly unused ID; vsDataType: Data type identifier; vsDataFormatVersion: Version of data format; EndpointResource.endpointResourceId: Resource ID; EndpointResource.userLabel: User-assigned label (mostly empty); EndpointResource.reservedBy:  String describing the resource reservation context (SubNetwork, MeContext, ManagedElement, Function).
